---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CronBuilder from '../tools/CronBuilder';
---
<Layout
  title="Cron Expression Builder & Tester"
  description="Build cron expressions visually and see the next 5 scheduled run times. Human-readable descriptions, common presets, and full cron syntax reference. Free online cron generator."
  keywords="cron expression builder, cron generator, crontab generator, cron schedule builder, cron tester online, cron expression generator, crontab guru"
>
  <CronBuilder client:load />
  <section class="seo-content">
    <h2>Free Online Cron Expression Builder</h2>
    <p>Build cron schedules visually without memorizing cron syntax. Select minutes, hours, days, months, and weekdays through an interactive interface. See a human-readable description and the next 5 scheduled run times calculated in real time.</p>
    <h3>Features</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Visual builder for each cron field (minute, hour, day, month, weekday)</li>
      <li>Common presets (hourly, daily, weekly, monthly)</li>
      <li>Next 5 run times calculated instantly</li>
      <li>Human-readable schedule description</li>
      <li>Raw expression editing with two-way sync</li>
      <li>Full cron format reference included</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Layout>
